			<div class="status">
				<div class="title">Adventurer Details</div>
				<div class="param">
					<ul>
						<li>A mysterious young man who wields powerful<br>winds. He claims to be a god of war sent by the<br>"keeper of fate." He speaks in an overly dramatic<br>fashion, clearly influenced by the poetry and<br>fiction he enjoys, but at his core he's a good guy.</li>
					</ul>
