				<span>Eternal Storm</span>
			</dt>
			<dd><div>Deals damage to enemies directly ahead,<br>and inflicts stormlash.<br>When the "Brewing Storm Lv. 5" effect is active,<br>a more powerful version of this skill will be used.</div><div class="skill-detail">Damage: 935 × 1 hit<br>Damage: 312 × 3 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 2,940<br>Special Effects:<br>・Stormlash<br>　　Lasts 21 seconds<br>　　Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>　　Damage: 41<br><br><color=#00008B>After Skill Change:</color><br>Damage: 125 × 8 hits<br>Damage: 500 × 2 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 2,940<br>Special Effects:<br>・Stormlash<br>　　Lasts 21 seconds<br>　　Triggers every 2.9 seconds<br>　　Damage: 41</div></dd><dt class="skill-cost-wrap"
				>
				<span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/273770323173fe0ea126abaf18c1b2352.png"></span>
