					</div>
				</div>
			</dt>
			<dd><div>Deals damage to multiple targets and enemies<br>near those targets, and draws them together.</div><div class="skill-detail">Damage: 300 × 9 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 8,640<br>Skill Energy Required (Shared Skill): 14,688<br></div></dd></dl></div>
