			<div class="status">
				<div class="title">Dragon Details</div>
				<div class="param">
					<ul>
						<li>A beguiling dragon with the regal aura of a<br>queen who prizes her beauty above all else.<br>Master of rose and briar, she lies in woodland<br>repose behind an impenetrable thorn wall of<br>her own creation.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div></div><div class="skill explanation">
	<div class="title">Skills</div>
	<dl><dt
				>
				<span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/120e337b87db017cf609bde65d5268d72.png"></span>
				<span>Sullen Rose</span>
			</dt>
			<dd><div>Deals damage to surrounding enemies,<br>and summons five enchanted roses.<br>These roses will deal damage to surrounding<br>enemies for 10 seconds before wilting,<br>then disappear after an additional 10 seconds.<br>Destroying a wilted rose will restore HP to<br>the user who destroyed it and count as having<br>defeated five enemies.</div><div class="skill-detail">Damage: 288 × 8 hits<br>Damage: 50 × 25 hits<br>Recovery Potency: 10 × 5</div></dd></dl></div><div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/87595b7438e74e5502d8b830d6bd16832.png"></span><span>(Wind) Strength +70%</span></dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Wind: <br>increases strength by 70%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/87595b7438e74e5502d8b830d6bd16832.png"></span><span>(Wind) Slayer's Strength +2%</span></dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Wind:<br>increases strength by 2% for every five enemies<br>defeated (up to five times per quest).</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>The stats shown here represent the dragon at maximum level, maximum bond, and fully unbound. They do not represent the stats when first obtained.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.</div><div>2. For a list of prizes and their appearance rates, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, and see Prizes under Appearance Rates.</div><div>3. If you obtain duplicate items from a tenfold summon or from using 10 single summon vouchers at once, the item quantities for each item will be combined when sent to the No Limit tab of your goodie box.</div><div>4. An Alberian Battle Royale skin for the adventurer featured in this summon showcase is now on sale and costs fewer items to unlock. Note that some adventurers do not have adventurer skins.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1620021600,update_time1619573463